6 hrs of live classes per class per week
80 students = 3 classes of 30-ish students each
Decision is not to include prep time in compensation.
So we need 1 STMs working 12 hours + 1 STM working 6 hours per week for each incoming SD class.
**Int'l SD 2 (May) STMs can transition to Int'l SD 4 (October)
**Int'l SD 3 (July) STMS can transition into Feb 2023 classes.
STM needs for Int'l for 2022 = 3 STMs working 12 hours a week.
